- app.py: Replace selectbox+pills nav with fixed sidebar navigation
  - Sidebar: brand block, radio nav (groups + sub-views), filters in sidebar
  - Remove emoji from all navigation labels
  - New page-header component (eyebrow + title + subtitle + live badge)
  - Complete CSS overhaul: Inter font, GHN orange accent, clean borders
  - All CSS classes renamed for clarity (pg-*, sb-*, sec-*, ai-*)

- shared/plotly_theme.py:
  - Rewrite make_html_kpi(): clean donut + label + value + delta (no emoji icons)
  - Add section_header() helper: accent bar + title + optional subtitle

- utils/ai_generator.py: Replace ✨ emoji icon with clean 'AI' text badge

- views/: Remove emoji from all section headers and page titles
  - company_overview, group_detail, org_drilldown, nlp_analysis,
    early_warning, action_priorities, deep_dive, hris_linkage
  - Duplicate group-name headings removed (now provided by app.py)
  - Section headers use new section_header() helper

- .streamlit/config.toml: Update background to #F8FAFC (light slate)

